Invocation Name: e. numbers
des:
Have you ever wondered what the E numbers listed on food packaging in the European Union actually are? now you can find out. Simply say Alexa, ask e numbers what is E1420. 

Please note that although every effort has been made to ensure this information is accurate and up to date you should not rely on this as a definitive or infallible source for information.
